    <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock screensteps-wrapper--introduction screensteps-wrapper">
  <div id="text-content_68385130-1D6F-0135-0EDA-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Self-enrollment can be enabled in account settings. Enabling self-enrollment give instructors the ability to allow students to use a join code or click a button to enroll themselves in a course. By default, self-enrollment is disabled for the account. </p>
<p>Once this feature is enabled, instructors can enable self-enrollment in Course Settings.</p>
  </div>
</div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_account" data-step-uuid="7688b275-714e-4903-94b2-5a34d97f254f">
    <h2 id="open_account" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Account</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/007/949/740/original/167b4d34-2e3f-4046-9aed-39673e67bdab.png" srcset="" alt="Open Account" height="542" width="453">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_683883A0-1D6F-0135-0EDC-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Global Navigation, click the <strong>Admin</strong> link [1], then click the name of the account [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="open_settings" data-step-uuid="1b97674a-d3cf-41aa-9828-13c20f9a7d0b">
    <h2 id="open_settings" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Open Settings</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/002/756/325/original/f91ed48c-8f75-4c57-89a1-682fe79a6057.png" srcset="" alt="Open Settings" height="282" width="188">
