  <div id="text-content_6838B0C0-1D6F-0135-0EDE-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In Account Settings, click the <strong>Settings</strong> link.  </p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="allow_self_enrollment" data-step-uuid="657328CA-7A83-417A-AD85-563E682CA56B">
    <h2 id="allow_self_enrollment" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Allow Self-Enrollment</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/000/791/327/original/7a2ac37f-4934-4d2f-be37-e475e1a4b0e2.png" srcset="" alt="Allow Self-Enrollment" height="82" width="450">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_6838DEB0-1D6F-0135-0EE0-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>In the Settings tab, locate the Allow Self-Enrollment drop-down menu.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="set_self_enrollment" data-step-uuid="ECB82C1F-108D-4CC1-94AC-3601D8DAB4AF">
    <h2 id="set_self_enrollment" class="step-title screensteps-heading">Set Self-Enrollment</h2>
        <div class="image screensteps-image">
      <img src="https://media.screensteps.com/image_assets/assets/001/619/699/original/f2522abc-ea31-49cb-a8fb-f35b6eb9b9c3.png" srcset="" alt="Set Self-Enrollment" height="84" width="292">
  </div>
 
      <div class="step-instructions screensteps-textblock">
  <div id="text-content_68390A70-1D6F-0135-0EE2-22000BC102FE" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Select the type of self-enrollment permission you want to enable. </p>
<p>To enable courses that aren’t linked to any SIS data or affected by SIS imports, click the <strong>For Manually-Created Courses </strong>option [1]. </p>
<p>To enable any type of course, whether manually-created or created using the SIS Import tool, click the <strong>For Any Courses</strong> option [2].</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
  </div>

      <div class="step screensteps-section screensteps-depth-1" id="update_settings" data-step-uuid="34E4334C-3B61-402D-9CFD-E867F506E17E">
